    {
        "content": "<p>At the very least you should put it on the arXiv, so people can easily find it and use its results and cite it.   This will help the world and even help you a bit.</p>",
        "id": 523377830,
        "sender_full_name": "John Baez",
        "timestamp": 1749592977
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>As for whether it's publishable, if it's a solid useful result and you feel you've proved it efficiently and written a clear, readable paper about it, I'd lean toward submitting it for publication and seeing what the referees think.</p>",
